Flatten Neighborhoods dropdown to a single alphabetized list

Drop the Florida Markets / Popup Detection Test Pages section headers
and dividers in favor of one plain dropdown listing all 28 USA
neighborhoods alphabetically, matching the original three-item style.
Also upgrade the 25 test pages from their minimal brand-only header to
the full site navbar, so QA can jump straight from one test page to the
next via the Neighborhoods dropdown without going back to an index.
